  "raw_meta_yaml": "{% set version = \"3.16.0\" %}\n{% set build = 2 %}\n\n# mpi must be defined for conda-smithy lint\n{% set mpi = mpi or 'nompi' %}\n\n# prefer nompi builds via a build number offset\n{% set build = build + 100 %}  # [mpi == 'nompi']\n{% set mpi_prefix = \"nompi\" %}  # [mpi == 'nompi']\n{% set mpi_prefix = \"mpi_\" + mpi %}  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n\n{% set tests_to_skip = \"_not_a_real_test\" %}\n{% set tests_to_skip = tests_to_skip + \" or test_multiprocess\" %}  # [('cp313t' in str(python)) or ('cp314t' in str(python))]\n\n# https://github.com/h5py/h5py/issues/2850\n{% set tests_to_skip = tests_to_skip + \" or test_ros3\" %}  # [win]\n\n{% set mpi_pytest_flag = \"\" %}\n{% set mpi_pytest_flag = \"--with-mpi\" %}  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n\npackage:\n  name: h5py\n  version: {{ version }}\n\nsource:\n  url: https://github.com/h5py/h5py/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz\n  sha256: 9c3aa5e1fc0c33ae8501a17987af2f986c8ba3ade25da66c78738a5abefea133\n  patches:\n    # Disable complex256 for arm64\n    # follow https://github.com/conda-forge/cross-python-feedstock/issues/92\n    - bad-numpy-patch.patch   # [osx and arm64]\n\nbuild:\n  number: {{ build }}\n  # add build string so packages can depend on\n  # mpi or nompi variants\n  # dependencies:\n  # `pkg * mpi_mpich_*` for mpich\n  # `hdf5 * mpi_*` for any mpi\n  # `hdf5 * nompi_*` for no mpi\n  string: {{ mpi_prefix }}_py{{ py }}h{{ PKG_HASH }}_{{ build }}\n  script_env:\n    - HDF5_HAS_ROS3=1  # [build_platform != target_platform]\n\nrequirements:\n  build:\n    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]\n    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]\n    - cython >=0.29.31,<4                    # [build_platform != target_platform]\n    - hdf5                                   # [build_platform != target_platform]\n    - hdf5 * {{ mpi_prefix }}_*              # [build_platform != target_platform]\n    - numpy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]\n    - {{ compiler(\"c\") }}\n    - {{ stdlib(\"c\") }}\n    - {{ mpi }}  # [mpi == 'openmpi' and build_platform != target_platform]\n  host:\n    - python\n    - pip\n    - setuptools\n    - numpy\n    - {{ mpi }}  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    - mpi4py >=3.0  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    # need to list hdf5 twice to get version pinning from conda_build_config\n    # and build pinning from {{ mpi_prefix }}\n    - hdf5\n    - hdf5 * {{ mpi_prefix }}_*\n    - cython >=0.29.31,<4\n    - pkgconfig\n  run:\n    - python\n    - cached-property\n    - {{ mpi }}  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    - mpi4py >=3.0  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    # hdf5 >=1.10.4 has run_exports\n    - hdf5\n\ntest:\n  imports:\n    - h5py\n    - h5py._conv\n    - h5py._errors\n    - h5py._objects\n    - h5py._proxy\n    - h5py.defs\n    - h5py.h5\n    - h5py.h5a\n    - h5py.h5d\n    - h5py.h5f\n    - h5py.h5fd\n    - h5py.h5g\n    - h5py.h5i\n    - h5py.h5l\n    - h5py.h5o\n    - h5py.h5p\n    - h5py.h5r\n    - h5py.h5s\n    - h5py.h5t\n    - h5py.h5z\n    - h5py.utils\n  commands:\n    {% set export = \"export\" %}   # [unix]\n    {% set export = \"set\" %}  # [not unix]\n    - {{ export }} AWS_REGION=us-east-2\n    - {{ export }} OMPI_MCA_plm=isolated  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    - {{ export }} OMPI_MCA_btl_vader_single_copy_mechanism=none  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    - {{ export }} OMPI_MCA_rmaps_base_oversubscribe=yes  # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    - pip check\n    - python -c \"import h5py; assert not h5py.get_config().mpi\"  # [mpi == 'nompi']\n    - python -c \"import h5py; assert h5py.get_config().mpi\"      # [mpi != 'nompi']\n    - python -m pytest --pyargs h5py {{ mpi_pytest_flag }} -k \"not ({{ tests_to_skip }})\"\n  requires:\n    - pip\n    - pytest\n    - pytest-mpi\n\nabout:\n  home: http://www.h5py.org/\n  license: BSD-3-Clause\n  license_file: licenses/license.txt\n  summary: Read and write HDF5 files from Python\n  dev_url: https://github.com/h5py/h5py\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - jan-janssen\n    - jakirkham\n    - tacaswell\n    - ocefpaf\n    - minrk\n    - scopatz\n",
